name: Sinclair Executive Electronic Pocket Calculator (1972) X-ray
description:
"Sinclair Executive" 1972 Electronic pocket calculator X-ray image. Radiated by Iñigo Bilbao. 2021. 2000x2000p. JPG.

World's first "slimline" pocket calculator and the first to be produced by Clive Sinclair's company Sinclair Radionics.
The Sinclair Executive was launched in September 1972 at the price of GB£79.95
